data.description: Welcome to your new home in the Chinook Townhouses complex! This contemporary townhouse offers the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience. This townhouse boasts 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with an open concept design, allowing for spacious living areas with vaulted ceilings that create an airy and inviting atmosphere. Step into the primary suite and wake up to stunning ocean views. The suite features a slider to the deck and a walk-in closet, providing ample space and natural light. Parking is a breeze with the oversized garage, which includes an enclosed storage room for added convenience. Enjoy deeded beach access, allowing you to embrace the coastal lifestyle to the fullest. Plus, access your home effortlessly with an elevator that connects the garage to the main level. Additionally, there are walkway and staircase options for added flexibility. This property offers a prime location near the beach, shopping, dining, and more.
